name: Alyssa Yu
location_string: Donsol, Sorsogon Province, Bicol Region, Luzon
description: I was born and raised in Legazpi City, an hour away from Donsol, Sorsogon where we'll be having the whaleshark encounter. Aside from having attended several seminars on whale shark interactions, I have swam with these gentle giants countless times and enjoyed it every single time! Because of this, I'd like other travelers to experience the same happiness and joy I felt interacting with these marine animals.
